{"tid":2498168,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【歐超聯】車路士場內場外都跪低　球迷狂歡 !!!!","createTime":"2021-04-21T03:49:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T03:49:45.000Z","uid":124655,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7b57b479d54b777b104dd954f5fb6f347f2662d8","tid":2498168,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:49:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20210421/photo/bkn-20210421084544738-0421_00882_001_01p.jpg?20210421091337\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20210421%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210421084544738-0421_00882_001_01p.jpg%3F20210421091337&h=cf54e6ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgresizer.eurosport.com/unsafe/1200x0/filters:format(jpeg):focal(1307x372:1309x370)/origin-imgresizer.eurosport.com/2021/04/20/3118171-63919148-2560-1440.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgresizer.eurosport.com%2Funsafe%2F1200x0%2Ffilters%3Aformat%28jpeg%29%3Afocal%281307x372%3A1309x370%29%2Forigin-imgresizer.eurosport.com%2F2021%2F04%2F20%2F3118171-63919148-2560-1440.jpg&h=4fe51d36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong>球迷: 仆街軌, 成班叻架</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n英超勁旅車路士周三(21日)宣布退出歐超聯，係英超6支球隊中第1隊發表退賽聲明嘅球隊，「藍戰士」周三凌晨主場迎戰白禮頓，開波前遇上大批憤怒球迷阻路，唔畀車路士嘅隊巴進入史丹福橋球場，要總監施治親自落車求球迷放行。雖然車路士最終主場被白禮頓悶和0比0痛失2分，但球隊隨後決定退出歐超聯，仍足以令一眾球迷瘋狂慶祝。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/J1Dgjjq4MqsdKyTSjs16fA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MC4zMTI1O2NmPXdlYnA-/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-04/38e36520-a242-11eb-bbeb-653f243a428e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FJ1Dgjjq4MqsdKyTSjs16fA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MC4zMTI1O2NmPXdlYnA-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2021-04%2F38e36520-a242-11eb-bbeb-653f243a428e&h=44d781c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong>施治: 俾條路黎行吓啦, 好嗎</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當車路士隊巴駛到球場備戰英超嗰陣，數百名憤怒車迷即衝出攔車抗議，要求班主阿布拉莫域退出歐超聯，車路士名將兼總監施治隨後落車安撫，不斷向球迷表示：「畀啲時間我哋處理。」但球迷就瘋狂喝倒采兼鬧佢係「叛徒」，最終隊巴都獲放行成功入場。激烈抗議入面有車迷被捕，亦有人向警察投擲啤酒樽，場面混亂。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://talksport.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/5/2021/04/TALKSPORT-Chelsea-3.jpg?strip=all&amp;quality=100&amp;w=1200&amp;h=800&amp;crop=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftalksport.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F5%2F2021%2F04%2FTALKSPORT-Chelsea-3.jpg%3Fstrip%3Dall%26quality%3D100%26w%3D1200%26h%3D800%26crop%3D1&h=9d64a5c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong>球迷: 打佢老母臭 gap !!! </strong></span><br />\n<br />\n車路士領隊杜曹喺賽前訪問表示，球員受到抗議事件影響未能集中精神，認為球員並冇任何錯誤，唔應該成為球迷出氣袋，結果車路士今場亦表現麻麻，被白禮頓悶和0比0，雖然仍能以得失球差壓住韋斯咸升上第4位，但對車路士嚟講仍然失去寶貴2分。"}]}